{
  "stem": "22892.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard the shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I-- he was a nice man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He used to tell me about the news.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would somehow-- he had us-- somebody would give him an old newspaper, a Ukrainian little newspaper.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when he finished it, he gave it-- he used to give it to me, the",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, maybe weeks old.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, but, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, it wasn't-- but you-- and the news were not-- you know, it was like-- but you could read between lines, figure things out.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, for instance, when the Germans were retreating, they would say-- I remember that word.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was [SPEAKING UKRAINIAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was in Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It means 'a planned retreat.' I was constantly-- when it was said-- I'd hear of 'planned retreats.'",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knew that the war may be going a different direction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But who knows how long it would take or anything like that?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I just-- you couldn't think of long term.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just wondered from day to day whether you're going to make it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are you going to survive?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or somebody, they'll get you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they were constantly hunting for, for Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How did you stay-- well, I don't know if you were healthy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But during the winter, were you always sick?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What, what was your physical condition?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was a time-- I've missed-- I missed part of that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was a time [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] that-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] you know that place that I told you we escaped [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from, where they-- you know, the last eight people were there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At one time, they came-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] it was a-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I have to think.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
